{"tid":2428233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國駐香港總領事館領事：國安法違反《中英聯合聲明》 非只針對一小撮人","createTime":"2021-03-01T11:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:56:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":118,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"b474ed4022372a950127304d8a60ea44769ad9c5","tid":2428233,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"47人因涉組織或參與去年民主派「35＋初選」被警方國安處以「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」起訴，案件今（3月1日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。數百名市民到庭外排隊聽審，包括歐盟、加拿大、美國、英國、荷蘭、德國及瑞典的外交官及領事館職員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國駐香港總領事館領事（政治及傳訊）韋俊輝表示，案件再次證明《港區國安法》用以消除政治異見，儘管香港與內地當局稱國安法只針對一小撮人，但今日47名民主派被檢控證明這說法不實，英方對此表示深切關注。韋俊輝表示，對本港司法系統非常有信心，但稱國安法違反《中英聯合聲明》。"},{"pid":"62750c2f814f88ef2773e1b5e9f2b9d689400038","tid":2428233,"uid":361751,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"可以派BC未？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f87a7e8746405fc6883d6ce7ea07675f47a2c8","tid":2428233,"uid":155431,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"中国：so?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94e15986ba976a1bc8be33a880b8ee0647015de","tid":2428233,"uid":207846,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"對本港司法系統非常有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9410f6233044e6cf3eff6803553087362666d4","tid":2428233,"uid":56015,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"e94e15986ba976a1bc8be33a880b8ee0647015de","tid":2428233,"uid":207846,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":